--- Asymmetric vs symmetric ---

Acrostic memory strategy used in the Security+ (Only need to memorise one to pass)

Asymmetric requires the same key to unlock

*ADDER*
*A*symmetric
*D*iffie-hellman
*D*SA
*E*CC
*R*SA

Symmetric requires 2 different keys to unlock

*STRAD*
*S*ymmetric
*T*wofish/blowfish
*R*C4
*A*ES
*D*ES

